2.2. Redistribution

You may reproduce and distribute copies of the Covered Software or
Modifications thereof that You develop or receive from You, in any
medium, with or without modifications, and in Source Code Form or
Executable Form, provided that You meet the following conditions:

(a) You must give any other recipients of the Covered Software, or
